committees met and their work I know that we call 
the aspirations committee we had what we called

06:12.783 --> 06:41.119
working parties to look at specific topics as 
those committees were doing their work do you

06:12.783 --> 06:41.119
remember much apprehension of anybody as to what 
the final recommendations might be from the

