President Rutter said, I'll tell you what we'll 
do. We'll take a team out to the University of

35:37.797 --> 35:54.781
California at Berkeley and visit their cyclotron 
Livermore Laboratories, see what's going on out

35:37.797 --> 35:54.781
there, what a cyclotron looks like, what it does.

35:57.564 --> 35:59.928
Let's get acquainted with a cyclotron.

36:02.291 --> 36:03.072
And so I was asked to go out there along with Tom 
Cherry, Fred Benson,

36:03.423 --> 36:13.998
